{"tid":2061071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想發動IG Event“612叉撚住”","createTime":"2020-06-12T06:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T06:22:34.000Z","uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9022bb17cea24c97fd636faa14af2dc5c7a84015","tid":2061071,"uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"相信唔少人每個月或隔段時間捐錢比612，但612仍然唔夠資金幫手足。有見及此，我想發動&ldquo;612叉撚住&rdquo; ig event。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望由宜家開始有捐錢比612嘅人，影張收據上ig動態，然後hashtag&ldquo;612叉撚住&rdquo;，當然一d私穩嘢例如名，金額同number要遮一遮。<br />\n<br />\n目的希望吸引到一d想捐錢但冇動力嘅人捐錢。hashtag嘅同時亦可以tag其他人，咁就大大增加活動成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但記得記得記得如果follower入面有藍絲frd的話就唔好做，驚你被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9add562fe089fadcd63b221f2e7ec99d18ba57","tid":2061071,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"On9"}]}